HEADWORD: Fleury
<hw>Fleur"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>fleuri</ets>
covered with flowers, p. p. of <ets>fleurir</ets>. See
<er>Flourish</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Finished at the ends
